# What NOT to publish to npm. The shipped package is the Klein interpreter +
# its contracts + bin + docs; everything below is development- or
# orchestration-only.

# Kernel orchestration scaffolding
SUBTASK_*/
**/_GLOBAL.md
**/_BRIEF.md
**/SUSPENSION.md
**/SYNTHESIS.md
**/COMPLETE.md
**/FAILURE.md

